---
// HowItWorks - 3-step detailed workflow grid
---

<section id="detailed-steps" class="section-padding bg-bg-secondary">
  <div class="container-main">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4">
      How It <span class="text-brand-red">Works</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="text-text-secondary text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
      Three simple steps to transform hours of editing into minutes
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- Step 01: Mark -->
      <div class="bg-bg-primary rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-800">
        <div class="text-brand-red font-mono text-sm mb-3">01</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Mark</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
          Press F9 (or your custom hotkey) anytime during gameplay. Flowmaster logs the timestamp in the background - no interruption, no overlay, no lag.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 02: Clip -->
      <div class="bg-bg-primary rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-800">
        <div class="text-brand-red font-mono text-sm mb-3">02</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Clip</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
          After your session, Clip scans for matching video files and extracts clips using a lookback window (default 30s before each mark). Batch process multiple recordings at once.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 03: Clean Up -->
      <div class="bg-bg-primary rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-800">
        <div class="text-brand-red font-mono text-sm mb-3">03</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Clean Up</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
          Once you've reviewed your highlights, Clean Up identifies the original raw footage and removes it with one click. Reclaim gigabytes of storage instantly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
